## Educational Use Notice

This project is specifically designed as an educational experiment in AI-first 
software development and father-son collaboration. While the code is freely 
available under the MIT License, we encourage educational use and adaptation 
for similar learning projects.

### Special Considerations for Educational Projects

- **Child Safety**: If adapting this project for use with children, please 
  review and implement appropriate safety measures as documented in our 
  comprehensive safety guidelines.

- **AI Content Moderation**: The AI agent interactions include multi-layer 
  content validation systems designed for child protection. These safety 
  measures should be maintained in any educational adaptation.

- **Real-World Data**: This project uses real World Bank GDP data and country 
  information for educational purposes. Please ensure accuracy and cultural 
  sensitivity in any adaptations.

### Attribution

If you use this project or its methodology in educational or research contexts, 
we would appreciate attribution to the original father-son AI collaboration 
experiment documented at https://worldleadersgame.co.uk

### Documentation License

The comprehensive documentation and methodology guides included in this project 
are also available under the MIT License, encouraging their use in educational 
technology research and development.
